================================================================================
    GTA5 Native 函数 C# 调用参考大全
================================================================================

数据来源: https://github.com/alloc8or/gta5-nativedb-data
文档用途: GTA5 模组开发 C# Native 调用参考
函数总数: 6673 个
命名空间: 45 个
最后更新: 2025年12月 (游戏版本 3717/1013)

================================================================================
                          使用说明
================================================================================

C# 调用 Native 的基本方式:

    using GTA;
    using GTA.Native;

    // 调用无返回值函数
    Function.Call(Hash.WAIT, 1000);

    // 调用有返回值函数
    Ped playerPed = Function.Call<Ped>(Hash.GET_PLAYER_PED, Game.Player);

    // 生成载具
    Vehicle vehicle = Function.Call<Vehicle>(Hash.CREATE_VEHICLE,
        (uint)VehicleHash.Adder,
        position.X, position.Y, position.Z,
        heading, false, false);

类型对照表:

    C++ 类型          C# 类型
    --------          --------
    void              void
    int               int
    float             float
    bool/BOOL         bool
    const char*       string
    Hash              uint
    Entity            int
    Ped               int
    Vehicle           int
    Object            int
    Player            int
    Cam               int
    Blip              int
    Any               object
    Any*              IntPtr
    Vector3           Vector3

[0x4EDE34FBADD967A6] void WAIT(int ms)
    C#: Function.Call(Hash.WAIT, ms);
    参数:
        - ms: int -> int
    说明: Pauses execution of the current script, please note this behavior is only seen when called from one of the game script files(ysc). In order to wait an asi script use "static void WAIT(DWORD time);" fo...

[0xE81651AD79516E48] int START_NEW_SCRIPT(const char* scriptName, int stackSize)
    C#: int result = Function.Call<int>(Hash.START_NEW_SCRIPT, scriptName, stackSize);
    参数:
        - scriptName: const char* -> string
        - stackSize: int -> int
    说明: Examples:  g_384A = SYSTEM::START_NEW_SCRIPT("cellphone_flashhand", 1424);  l_10D = SYSTEM::START_NEW_SCRIPT("taxiService", 1828);  SYSTEM::START_NEW_SCRIPT("AM_MP_YACHT", 5000);  SYSTEM::START_NEW_SC...

[0xB8BA7F44DF1575E1] int START_NEW_SCRIPT_WITH_ARGS(const char* scriptName, Any* args, int argCount, int stackSize)
    C#: int result = Function.Call<int>(Hash.START_NEW_SCRIPT_WITH_ARGS, scriptName, args, argCount, stackSize);
    参数:
        - scriptName: const char* -> string
        - args: Any* -> object*
        - argCount: int -> int
        - stackSize: int -> int
    说明: return : script thread id, 0 if failed Pass pointer to struct of args in p1, size of struct goes into p2

[0xEB1C67C3A5333A92] int START_NEW_SCRIPT_WITH_NAME_HASH(Hash scriptHash, int stackSize)
    C#: int result = Function.Call<int>(Hash.START_NEW_SCRIPT_WITH_NAME_HASH, scriptHash, stackSize);

        - stackSize: int -> int

[0x83666F9FB8FEBD4B] int TIMERA()
    C#: int result = Function.Call<int>(Hash.TIMERA);
    说明: Counts up. Every 1000 is 1 real-time second. Use SETTIMERA(int value) to set the timer (e.g.: SETTIMERA(0)).

    C#: float result = Function.Call<float>(Hash.VMAG, x, y, z);
    参数:
        - x: float -> float
        - y: float -> float
        - z: float -> float
    说明: Calculates the magnitude of a vector.

[0xA8CEACB4F35AE058] float VMAG2(float x, float y, float z)
    C#: float result = Function.Call<float>(Hash.VMAG2, x, y, z);
    参数:
        - x: float -> float
        - y: float -> float
        - z: float -> float
    说明: Calculates the magnitude of a vector but does not perform Sqrt operations. (Its way faster)

[0x2A488C176D52CCA5] float VDIST(float x1, float y1, float z1, float x2, float y2, float z2)
    C#: float result = Function.Call<float>(Hash.VDIST, x1, y1, z1, x2, y2, z2);

        - y1: float -> float
        - z1: float -> float
        - x2: float -> float
        - y2: float -> float
        - z2: float -> float
    说明: Calculates distance between vectors.

        - z2: float -> float
    说明: Calculates distance between vectors but does not perform Sqrt operations. (Its way faster)
